    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>Stage 1 of Grafvitnir's manifestation — a massive black wolf that fills the longhouse with its presence, eyes burning green with rot-light. Though still fundamentally wolf-shaped, the corruption has stretched it beyond natural scale into something ancient and terrible. In Stage 1, Grafvitnir tests the heroes' patterns with a Howl of Binding that can lock heroes in place, a devastating Lunge across the battlefield, and a Rot Breath that spreads corruption across wide areas. 200 Hit Points, Huge. Two turns per round.</p>",
